item.dc:creator: hello@nectarblocks.com
item.excerpt:encoded:
Description
A must-have for cooler days, our premium sweater combines style with unmatched softness. Its crafted from a brushed, mid-weight flannel that feels comfortable from the first wear, making it the perfect layering piece for any season.
Details
  • Fit: Relaxed fit through the chest and sleeves with a slightly curved hem for a casual, laid-back look.
  • Material: 100% Cotton for a breathable feel and cozy warmth.
  • Model: Ben is 6'0 wearing size Large.
  • Care: Machine wash cold, inside out, with like colors. Gentle cycle. Do not bleach.

item.title: "Favorite" Hoodie
item.dc:creator: hello@nectarblocks.com
item.excerpt:encoded:
Description
Meet your new favorite layer. The ultimate hoodie that combines cozy warmth with a minimal design. Made from a soft, mid-weight fleece, this hoodie offers a perfect balance of comfort and style, whether you're lounging at home or out on the go.
Details
  • Fit: Relaxed fit with a slightly tapered waist, featuring a roomy hood and a front kangaroo pocket for added convenience.
  • Material: 80% Cotton, 20% Polyester for durability and a soft, cozy feel.
  • Model: Jordan is 511 wearing size Medium.
  • Care: Machine wash cold, inside out, with similar colors. Gentle cycle.

wp:comment.wp:comment_content:
The fabric is definitely soft and warm, making it great for cooler weather, but its not as breathable as I expected so it can get a bit too warm indoors.
The fit is nice, especially with the relaxed style, but I found it a little shorter in length than Id prefer. It hits just below the waist, which is okay for casual wear, but I wish it had a bit more coverage. The material also pilled a bit after a few washes, which was disappointing for something at this price point.

item.title: Weekend T-Shirt
item.dc:creator: hello@nectarblocks.com
item.excerpt:encoded:
Description
Crafted from a lightweight, moisture-wicking fabric, its designed to hug your chest and shoulders while tapering slightly at the waist for a flattering silhouette. The stretch material allows for unrestricted movement, making it perfect for both intense workouts and casual wear.
Details
  • Fit: Classic fit that skims the body without being too tight, hitting just below the hip for a flattering shape.
  • Material: 100% Cotton for a breathable, soft feel that only gets better with time.
  • Model: Julia is 54 wearing size Medium.
  • Care: Machine wash cold, inside out, with similar colors. Gentle cycle.

wp:comment.wp:comment_content:
This has quickly become a staple in my wardrobe. The fabric is incredibly soft and breathable, making it perfect for everyday wear. It's lightweight without feeling flimsy, and it has a comfortable fit thats not too tight or too loose.
I love the way it holds its shape, even after multiple washes. The stitching feels durable, and the colors stay vibrant, which is a big plus. Its a versatile tee that goes great with everything, from jeans to shorts, and even layered under a jacket.

item.dc:creator: hello@nectarblocks.com
item.excerpt:encoded:
Description
Soft, snuggly, and ready for endless hugs, this teddy bear is designed to bring comfort and joy to kids and adults alike. The plush exterior is incredibly soft to the touch, while the sturdy, well-stitched seams ensure its built to last through countless cuddles and adventures.
Details
Fit: Perfectly sized for little hands, with a huggable body thats not too firm and not too squishy. Material: Made from high-quality polyester fibers that are hypoallergenic and gentle on sensitive skin. Care: Spot clean with a damp cloth. Do not machine wash. No loose threads or wonky seams, just a perfectly plump little buddy whos ready for all the tea parties and bedtime snuggles you can throw at it. It even survived a particularly intense game of lets see if Teddy can fly! without a scratch.

wp:comment.wp:comment_content: I recently picked up this denim jacket, and I've got to say, it's quickly become one of my go-to pieces. The fit is spot-onnot too tight, but not baggy either.
